                    <h2 data-uuid="4e7e9e9f5ca4488b867fbb57cbb7bb73">The Big Idea</h2>
                    <p data-uuid="8c0cab4e774e45949788765bb73336c8">The movement to end slavery was the most
                        prominent and divisive effort of reform in the United States in the mid-1800s.</p>
