            <article data-uuid="93aaf0305f114c6999adc4a93b68bc23">
                <h3 class="if-you-were-there" data-uuid="6a6ad3793f2240f588ea8d9db68d1927">If YOU were there...</h3>
                <p data-uuid="8abae60f5c8d467285a6c832589415c5">You live in South
                    Carolina in the 1850s. You are invited by a friend to hear Angelina and Sarah
                    Grimk&#233;, two southerners fighting to abolish slavery, speak at your friendâ€™s
                    house. Your father is a slaveholder, and you know he disapproves of abolition
                    and the Grimk&#233; sisters. You are interested in hearing what they have to say.
                    But you know this might get you in trouble with your father and other family
                    members.</p>
